@startuml
!theme plain
actor User
component "QAlite SPA" as App
cloud "Firebase Auth" as Auth
database "Firestore" as Firestore
folder "Firebase Storage" as Storage
cloud "Slack Webhook" as Slack

User -> App : login, CRUD, execução
App -> Auth : autenticar/observar sessão
App -> Firestore : ler/gravar domínio
App -> Storage : upload de arquivos
Storage --> App : downloadURL
App -> Firestore : grava URL da evidência/logo/foto
App -> Slack : POST resumo formatado
@enduml
